ANTIPHON
-
~To express my happy mood
~I haven't found any good,
~Optimistic rhimes on "weather"
~For example, "there" or "leather".
~So, I'd like to say that spring,
~With its wind that cools the skin,
~With its murmours of the grass,
~With the boy which thinks of lass,
~Makes me sing and makes me love,
~Makes me look at sky above.
